===== Generate an entity =====
Use php app/console generate:doctrine:entity to generate an entity
Choose "annotation" as a configuration format.
Say "yes" to "Do you want to generate an empty repository class [no]?".

Use php app/console generate:doctrine:crud to automagically generate the controller, view files and forms.
Say "yes" to "Do you want to generate the "write" actions [no]?".
Choose "yml" as a configuration format.
Say "yes" to "Confirm automatic update of the Routing [yes]?".

===== Indentation =====
Always use 2 spaces to indent.
Use 4 spaces for YAML files.
